{"tid":594023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[笑到肚痛]的士司機鐵錘打爛車抗議白牌車 一司機受傷","createTime":"2018-03-15T13:06:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T15:35:23.000Z","uid":33890,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"458f44d22ceeb788ca1d46549f141e20a3b1032d","tid":594023,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T13:06:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20150724/54011690\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20150724%2F54011690&d=HJ3VHFVOi4atUZKNgWQtTKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=7e019cf3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20150724%2F54011690&h=d0e66280\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20150724/54011690</a><br />\n電召車手機應用程式大行其道，當中不少為「白牌」豪華房車，惹起的士業界不滿。汽車交通運輸業總工會的士司機分會、城市的士車主司機聯會及新界的士司機聯會今日於灣仔入境事務大樓外示威，以鐵錘打爛一輛的士，表達業界不滿及要求全面取締白牌車，期間一名的士司機受傷。<br />\n<br />\n示威者高舉「強烈要求政府保障守法司機生計」及「要求政府加強執法」等標語，並打爛車窗、車頭燈及車頭冚。代表又將咪錶交還運輸署，諷刺按表收費名存實亡。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e70a6509dde84e4bc6b90a2599aee3c15b086667","tid":594023,"uid":6752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T13:08:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e681920d5cb8aa7d68fff0e965762bcbe47d63ae","tid":594023,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T13:10:52.000Z",